review_title: fun but shame its not full multiplayer
one_reviews_text: Theres a lack of PC Vs VR games and this would have been a really fun one to play with friends not locally
its the best party game that i played you can play with your family and it has a mode for the kids its super!! :3

great fun with a group of friends, even those that have never played vr. Definetly a must for any vr user
only thing it needs (which im sure are on the way) is more maps and maybe bots or when you only have a small group
Great party game. It needs alot more maps. 5 maps are not gonna be enough btw.
Great party game.  Finally a game that doen't involve everyone just staring at a person wearing a VR headset.  More levels please!
